creator: Hula Partners
descriptionHtml:
Kahuna is the only competency management solution designed especially for the people who manage day to day operations. The Kahuna mobile app allows these leaders to manage their team from their own personal mobile device.

• This new app will allow users to access Kahuna from anywhere in the world. An internet connection is not required.

• The user can store assessment data and learning history and then upload it to Kahuna online when connected.

• Users can access their Kahuna profile at any time in any place.

• Supervisors can perform assessments and track employee experience from their mobile device.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
# Switch ability added to the device register page
# General bug fixes and enhancements
